properties.Name: ReadingErrorType
properties.Description:
A type of reading error that is associated with a component.

Ex:
- Equipment Failure
- Communication Failure
- Friction Error
- Creeping Error
- Temperature Error
- Speed Error
- Calibration Error
- Miscellaneous Error
